You can embed custom HTML using <html> inside a panel using type="html".

Example Dashboard Snippet:
<dashboard>
  <label>HTML Panel Example</label>
  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
        <![CDATA[
          <div style="padding:10px; background-color:#f8f8f8; border:1px solid #ccc;">
            <h2 style="color:#0072c6;">Welcome to Splunk Dashboard!</h2>
            <p>This is a custom HTML block. You can style it as needed.</p>
          </div>
        ]]>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
</dashboard>
